### Backend (Firebase Only)
- Firebase Firestore (database + real-time)
- Firebase Auth (admin login)
- Firebase Hosting (optional)

### Utilities
- qrcode.react (QR generation)
- nanoid (IDs)

### Styling / UI
- Vanilla CSS

